item.title: About
item.description: My name is Sebastián Mora, I am computer engineering student at ITCR. I’m a young programmer passionate about building solutions in a variety of programming languages and frameworks. Constantly trying to improve my skills as a software developer. I’m interested in web development, either front-end or back-end, low level programming, arduino and cloud computing.
